{"tid":970850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【尋狗】無人係深水步/長沙灣交界，見過一隻白內障既芝娃娃？","createTime":"2019-01-06T07:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T14:04:35.000Z","uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"883fa9b45e5943ba40ce3235ab6f5f15f3225b9a","tid":970850,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"我好幾年前見過佢，係「九龍工業學校」同電話機樓果頭。有個阿婆帶住出街既。<br />\n<br />\n聽阿婆講，芝娃娃有嚴重白內障。視力得返好少。<br />\n<br />\n有無手足近日有見過佢地？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a887823c39366eaec19a709062e3265993ed532c","tid":970850,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf17902e03c331fd81aa57a498b4cff8eb91c5a","tid":970850,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9967095df52d267d180addc1f0b1e60321829a93","tid":970850,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:46:54.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"29795096831de430bcdab70e1facdb2072742a54","tid":970850,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T08:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5922b8f28120fe04659ded35e5e077d3edb4e4","tid":970850,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}